<item>
            <title>[GROOVY-5160] Assignments in if/else/for/while/ternary are not type checked properly</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/GROOVY-5160</link>
                <project id="12318123" key="GROOVY">Groovy</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The following code will pass, though the return type of x after the if/else statement may differ:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;def x
&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; (cond) {
  x = &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;new&lt;/span&gt; Date()
} &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;else&lt;/span&gt; {
  x = 123
}
x.toInteger()
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;In a similar manner:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;def x = &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;123&apos;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;for&lt;/span&gt; (&lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;int&lt;/span&gt; i=0; i&amp;lt;5;i++) { x = &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;new&lt;/span&gt; HashSet() }
x.toInteger()
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;def x = &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;123&apos;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;while&lt;/span&gt; (&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;false&lt;/span&gt;) { x = &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;new&lt;/span&gt; HashSet() }
x.toInteger()
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;def x = &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;123&apos;&lt;/span&gt;
def cond = &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;false&lt;/span&gt;
cond?(x = &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;new&lt;/span&gt; HashSet()):3
x.toInteger()
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
